1. *Začepio* je vrata svoje kuće. (He locked the door of his house.)
2. Otac je *začepio* svoje sina u sobi. (The father locked his son in the room.)
3. On je *začepio* svoje srce za zaljubljenost. (He locked his heart against love.)
4. Ona je *začepila* svoju ljubav prema njemu. (She locked away her love for him.)
5. On je *začepio* svoju prošlost. (He locked away his past.)
6. Oni su *začepili* njenu sudbinu. (They sealed her fate.)